Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.12,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}毫不留情 不知何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.54,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}一旦迷失前进指标 就会狂暴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:43.95,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Pay attention！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.20,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Hey one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.46,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Hey what is it？Watch your step now！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.25,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}并不需要常识
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:48.96,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.92,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}No No No don't worry  One Two Three
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.13,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}沉默的心脏 再次传来跳动的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:58.38,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}即使视野很混乱 但是不得不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:05.52,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}你还相信着 我不会背叛你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.64,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}震撼地号角声鸣起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:11.31,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}即使孤单着 就算时光变迁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.69,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}还是学会逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.99,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}崭新的一天还会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:21.41,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}这个愿望 即使没有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.49,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}我也誓要实现它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.95,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}我们彼此还有众多憧憬的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.37,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}所以即使想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:33.34,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}还是心有不甘 也不能止步不前
